HEADWORD: brisance
<hw>bri"sance</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>the shattering or crushing effect
of a sudden release of energy as in an explosion; -- used especially as
a measure of such a shattering power, applied to high
explosives.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source> <source>+PJC</source>]</p>

